# Refund Policy

**Effective Date:** July 10, 2025  
**App Name:** ApiaryAI  
**Developer:** Daniel Najda Pty Ltd  
**Contact:** danielnajda@danielnajda.com

---

## Overview

ApiaryAI offers a one-time in-app purchase to unlock all premium features.  
All purchases are processed through the **Apple App Store** or **Google Play Store** and are subject to the refund policies of those platforms.

---

## Apple App Store Refunds

If you made your purchase through the Apple App Store, you must request a refund directly from Apple.  
Apple handles all transactions and refund requests independently of ApiaryAI.

To request a refund:
- Visit [https://reportaproblem.apple.com](https://reportaproblem.apple.com)
- Sign in with your Apple ID
- Locate the purchase and follow the instructions to request a refund

---

## Google Play Store Refunds

If you made your purchase through Google Play:
- You may be eligible for a refund if requested within 48 hours
- Visit [https://play.google.com/store/account](https://play.google.com/store/account)
- Click "Order History"
- Locate the item and choose "Request a refund"

Google processes all payments and refunds on their own terms.

---

## No Direct Refunds

As a developer, we do **not have access** to your payment information or the ability to issue direct refunds.  
All requests must be handled through Apple or Google per their respective policies.

---

